        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Cloud-Centric Approach"
        },
        {
          "t": "p",
          "text": "With Azure, you can deploy virtual machines for Windows and Linux, modernize your applications, and develop apps that work seamlessly across cloud and hybrid environments."
